🩸 Blood Donor Management System 📌 Overview

A web-based application that helps users find blood donors quickly and efficiently. It allows users to register as donors and search for blood based on group and location.

🎯 Features Donor registration and login Search donors by blood group and city View donor details Admin can manage donor records

🛠️ Technologies Used Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Backend: Java (Servlets, JSP), JDBC

Database: MySQL

Tools: Eclipse IDE, Apache Tomcat

⚙️ How It Works User registers as a donor Data is stored in MySQL database Users search donors based on requirements Admin manages records

💡 Purpose To provide a fast and reliable way to connect blood donors with patients during emergencies.

